OL,3,CConcern over the state of local roads
OL,4,Creaches record high
OL,6,FConcern about the state of local roads
OL,7,Fhas reached record levels, with more
OL,8,Fthan half of motorists saying it was a
OL,9,Ftop worry for the first time, new
OL,10,Fresearch by the RAC has found.
OL,12,FMore than half of drivers (56%) said
OL,13,Fthe condition and maintenance of roads
OL,14,Ffor which councils are responsible was
OL,15,Fone of their top motoring concerns.
