OL,3,CConcern over the state of local roads
OL,4,Creaches record high
OL,6,FThat is up seven percentage points
OL,7,Ffrom 2023, and is the first time the
OL,8,Ffigure has been above 50% since the
OL,9,Fmotoring services company began
OL,10,Fincluding the topic in its annual poll
OL,11,Fin 2015.
OL,13,FNearly three out of four (73%)
OL,14,Frespondents to the latest survey said
OL,15,Fthe condition of the local roads they
OL,16,Fuse regularly was poorer than a year
OL,17,Fearlier, compared with 67% who agreed
OL,18,Fwith that statement in 2023.
OL,20,FThe figure rose to 81% for drivers in
OL,21,Frural areas.
