OL,3,CConcern over the state of local roads
OL,4,Creaches record high
OL,6,FSome 27% of those questioned said
OL,7,Ftheir vehicle suffered damage as a
OL,8,Fresult of potholes in the previous 12
OL,9,Fmonths.
OL,11,FThe most common problem reported was a
OL,12,Fpuncture (47%), followed by wheel
OL,13,Fdamage (43%) and broken suspension
OL,14,Fsprings (29%).
OL,16,FThe RAC has written to Transport
OL,17,FSecretary Louise Haigh and Roads
OL,18,FMinister Lilian Greenwood calling for
OL,19,Furgent clarification on the future of
OL,20,Flocal road maintenance funding.
