OL,3,CConcern over the state of local roads
OL,4,Creaches record high
OL,6,FRAC head of policy Simon Williams
OL,7,Fsaid: "These new figures are a damning
OL,8,Fcondemnation of the commitments made
OL,9,Fby previous governments to fix
OL,10,FBritain's perpetual pothole plague.
OL,12,F"It's as clear as day that councils
OL,13,Fsimply haven't had the financial
OL,14,Fsupport they need to bring the
OL,15,Fstandard of the roads in their care up
OL,16,Fto a reasonable standard.
