OL,6,F"It is absolutely remarkable that, on
OL,7,Faverage, drivers we surveyed are far
OL,8,Fmore concerned about the state of
OL,9,Ftheir local roads this year than they
OL,10,Fare about either the cost of motor
OL,11,Finsurance ` which has been rocketing
OL,12,Fin recent years ` or the cost of fuel
OL,13,Fwhich is still at an uncomfortably
OL,14,Fhigh level."
