OL,3,CConcern over the state of local roads
OL,4,Creaches record high
OL,6,FIn October 2023, the Conservative
OL,7,Fgovernment announced it would provide
OL,8,F#8.3 billion of extra funding over 11
OL,9,Fyears to fix potholes in England.
OL,11,FThis was part of its Network North
OL,12,Fstrategy to use money saved by
OL,13,Fscrapping the planned extension of HS2
OL,14,Fnorth of Birmingham.
OL,16,FA Department for Transport
OL,17,Fspokesperson said: "Rebuilding Britain
OL,18,Fmeans modernising our transport
OL,19,Finfrastructure, and we are absolutely
OL,20,Fcommitted to tackling the poor state
OL,21,Fof our local roads.
